            "block_description": "<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1714379818996666/posts/2150493462051964\" target=\"_blank\">My neighbor lent his de-thatcher for a test with my Yarbo. Enjoy this short video of me, scratching my grass…&gt;&gt;&gt;</a></p>",
