            "block_description": "<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1714379818996666/posts/2131114200656557/\" target=\"_blank\">An hour away from home, spending time with family and enjoying the birthday party. Meanwhile Yarbo works faithfully and tirelessly mowing my lawn. Now my only problem is...&gt;&gt;&gt;</a></p>",
            "block_image": "shopify://shop_images/Mask-group-_14_-0.webp",
